<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Currently filter will apply to all array values throw array_walk_recursive:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
    public function getValue()
    {
        $valueFiltered = $this-&gt;_value;

        if (is_array($valueFiltered)) {
            array_walk_recursive($valueFiltered, array($this, '_filterValue'));
        } else {
            $this-&gt;_filterValue($valueFiltered, $valueFiltered);
        }

        return $valueFiltered;
    }
</code></pre>

<p>Can you add $this-&gt;isArray() to condition to filter array values only when $this-&gt;isArray() set to true...</p>

